        public ScmChangeFileDto(ScmChangeSetDto changeSet,
                java.lang.String change,
                java.lang.String oldRevision,
                java.lang.String copyPath)
        Create an ScmChangeFileDto from a change specification string
        Parameters:
        changeSet - is the change set this change belongs to
        change - is the change specification string "{+|-|*}dirName/fileName[#revision]"
        oldRevision - is the old revision of the (modified file)
        copyPath - is the path to the original when a file was copied/moved.
        Since:
        CB-7.1.1
